 The Weeknd 打破温布利球场门票销售记录https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-销售记录Liberty DunworthMon, 21 Aug 2023 12:29:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3486018 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位创作歌手今年早些时候还打破了伦敦体育场最高上座率记录</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018">《The Weeknd》打破温布利球场门票销售记录的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-