35664874/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>采访时表示：“令人难以置信的是，《Weeknd》在欧洲巡演的门票全部售罄的情况下不到一半就达到了这一里程碑。” “伦敦的这一历史性时刻展示了他多年来培养的全球粉丝基础。”</p><p> CAA 北美巡演联席主管达里尔·伊顿 (Darryl Eaton) 对此表示同意，并补充道：“我们非常自豪能够与他和他的团队合作进行这次令人难以置信的巡演！”</p><p>据 Live Nation 当时的报道（ <a href="https://hiphopdx.com/news/weeknd-smashes-record-london-wembley-stadium" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>HipHopDX</em></a>报道），Tesfaye 的全球巡演迄今为止已累积了约 3.5 亿美元（274,854,650 英镑）。现在，在温布利的欧洲站结束后，这位音乐家、词曲作者和演员将开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-announces-2023-uk-european-and-latin-america-tour-3356866">他在南美洲和墨西哥举行的剩余演出</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3440834" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3440834" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3440834" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new.jpg" alt="周末" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/The-Weeknd-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3440834" class="wp-caption-text">周末。图片来源：Axelle/Bauer-Griffin/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>该媒体还报道称，余下的现场演出门票已售出超过 200 万张，演出将于 9 月 25 日在墨西哥蒙特雷的 Estadio BBVA 拉开帷幕，并于 10 月在墨西哥瓜达拉哈拉的 Estadio Akron 举行最后一场演出。 25. <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-weeknd-tickets%2Fartist%2F1697014" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>查找门票。</p><p>在其他消息中，The Weeknd 最近 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-confirms-he-is-finishing-his-new-album-3461572">证实他正在“完成”他的新专辑</a>，该专辑将结束以<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“After Hours”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“Dawn FM”</a>为特色的三部曲。</p><p>在其他地方，早在 3 月份，Tesfaye 就被<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>统计<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-named-the-worlds-most-popular-artist-3418082">评为全球最受欢迎的艺术家</a>——当时每月有 1.114 亿听众。</p><p>就在几周前，这位音乐家成为 Spotify 历史上第一位月听众人数突破 1 亿的艺人， <a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2023/3/the-weeknd-is-officially-the-worlds-most-popular-artist-741774" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>吉尼斯世界纪录</em></a>分享了这份报告。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018">《The Weeknd》打破温布利球场门票销售记录的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
