uchTunes 数字点唱机上播放，并附有其潜在的艺术作品。</p><p>猜测罗斯和同事。可能会在今年早些时候正式发行这首歌，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-soundcheck-unreleased-song-perhaps-ahead-of-israel-concert-watch-footage-3452517">粉丝们在特拉维夫等待观看乐队，无意中听到成员们在演出前排练“也许”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-tease-another-new-song-the-general-set-to-arrive-in-october-3485958">Guns N&#39; Roses 的另一首新歌“The General”将于 10 月发布，该歌曲</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ;
